metadata.title: Complete 256 Odu System - Matrix Excel Integration

cards.name: OGBE
cards.pattern:
MEJI
II
II
II
II
cards.guidance: The wisdom of OGBE brings light, clarity, divine wisdom. Trust in this divine guidance.
cards.guidanceYoruba: Ọgbọ́n OGBE ni kí a gbà. Àṣẹ!
cards.proverb: Through OGBE, we find the path to spiritual understanding.
cards.proverbYoruba: Nípasẹ̀ OGBE, a rí ọ̀nà sí òye ẹ̀mí.
cards.modernApplication: Apply the teachings of OGBE in daily spiritual practice.
cards.traditionalStory: In the ancient tradition, OGBE was revealed to guide humanity.
